==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: detoxify
<hw>detoxify</hw> <pos>v. t.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>to remove poison
from; to rid of the effects of poison.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> detoxicate.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>to render (a poisonous substance) non-toxic or
harmless.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>detoxification</ent>⟦br⟧
